{"id":3397,"date":"2023-08-17T16:52:55","date_gmt":"2023-08-17T09:52:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/?p=3397"},"modified":"2023-10-12T16:27:09","modified_gmt":"2023-10-12T09:27:09","slug":"tim-hieu-ve-xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/tim-hieu-ve-xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e0i loan t\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 du h\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, Smart Way &#8211; trung t\u00e2m t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n du h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>I. T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Gi\u1ea3m chi ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp:<\/strong> Nh\u1eadn h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n chi ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u0103n h\u00f3a m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3399\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3399\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3399\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/12-1692265850.jpg\" alt=\"xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/12-1692265850.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/12-1692265850-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3399\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p:<\/strong> M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin, kinh t\u1ebf, y t\u1ebf, ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c. Nh\u1eadn h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf:<\/strong> Du h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng \u0110\u00e0i Loan cung c\u1ea5p c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 giao l\u01b0u v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi quan h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">II. \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng. Sinh vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t, v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh cao trong c\u00e1c n\u0103m h\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IELTS t\u1eeb 5.5 tr\u1edf l\u00ean ho\u1eb7c TOEIC t\u1eeb 700 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng) \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TOCFL c\u1ea5p 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Trung.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3400\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3400\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3400\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1692265849.jpg\" alt=\"dieu-kien-xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1692265849.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1692265849-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3400\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u01b0 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u01b0 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1eeb gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n. Th\u01b0 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i du h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i lu\u1eadn: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u sinh vi\u00ean vi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 l\u00fd do mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: Sinh vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m, gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd li\u00ean quan kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u00ean, c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cung c\u1ea5p h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n kh\u00e1c nhau. Vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n xin l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>III. C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 \u0110\u00e0i Loan:<\/strong> Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 \u0110\u00e0i Loan cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, bao g\u1ed3m h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng to\u00e0n ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0 b\u00e1n ph\u1ea7n. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean ti\u00eau ch\u00ed nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc:<\/strong> Nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u0169ng cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng ri\u00eang cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean th\u00e0nh t\u00edch h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3401\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3401\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3401\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/13-1692265850.jpg\" alt=\"cac-loai-hoc-bong\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/13-1692265850.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/13-1692265850-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3401\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">IV. C\u00e1ch xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>N\u1eafm v\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin:<\/strong> T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, bao g\u1ed3m ti\u00eau ch\u00ed, quy tr\u00ecnh xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3). \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/strong> Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd nh\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p, \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, th\u01b0 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u, b\u00e0i lu\u1eadn, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3386\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3386\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3386\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/10-1692178110.jpg\" alt=\"chuan-bi-ho-so\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/10-1692178110.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/10-1692178110-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3386\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i lu\u1eadn thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c:<\/strong> B\u00e0i lu\u1eadn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng. H\u00e3y vi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i lu\u1eadn ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, t\u1ea3 r\u00f5 l\u00fd do b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>V. L\u01b0u \u00fd khi xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/strong> Lu\u00f4n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng. Tr\u1ec5 h\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung:<\/strong> \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3402\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3402\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3402\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/11-1692265850.jpg\" alt=\"luu-y-khi-xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/11-1692265850.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/11-1692265850-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3402\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>L\u01b0u \u00fd khi xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0110\u00e0i Loan:<\/strong> Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, h\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan. <\/span>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/\">Smart Way<\/a>. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Fanpage:\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/duhocsmartway\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Du h\u1ecdc Smart Way<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Email:<\/strong>\u00a0\u00a0duhocsmartway@gmail.com<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hotline:\u00a0<\/strong>0983.741.042 \u2013 0988.108.164<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:\u00a0<\/strong>S\u1ed1 27, li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 12, Khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb V\u0103n Kh\u00ea, Ph\u01b0\u1eddng La Kh\u00ea, Qu\u1eadn H\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":3403,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[11,40,46],"class_list":["post-3397","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-cam-nang-du-hoc","tag-du-hoc-dai-loan","tag-hoc-bong","tag-xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3397","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/17"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3397"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3397\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3404,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn